  "texts": [
    "For example, in the spatial-temporal prediction of traffic flow, dynamic graph processing plays an indispensable role in this field.",
    "Since the traffic flow and congestion level in a traffic network continue to evolve, the graph pooling operation becomes a crucial step.",
    "It is capable of simplifying and extracting high-level abstract representations of dynamically changing traffic network graphs (Jin et al. 2307).",
    "In this process, graph pooling not only needs to cope with the dynamic changes of the traffic network but also ensure that key spatial-temporal information is not lost in the process of simplified representation.",
    "Such a processing operation can not only improve the efficiency of the prediction model but also significantly enhance the accuracy of the prediction results, providing strong support for traffic management decisions (Kazemi et al. 2020)."
  ],
